Package: pocketlogR
Title: Log Application Events to PocketBase from R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Quinten", "Goens", email = "qgoens@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A unified operational monitoring system that logs application events
    (data jobs, website monitoring, email checks, database checks, etc.) to a
    PocketBase instance. Supports DAG-based flow dependencies with cascade health
    checks and two authentication modes (regular user and superuser).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    cli
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/euctrl-pru/pocketlogR
